    <item>
      <title>驱逐中国学生引起耶鲁大学和弗吉尼亚大学混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-05-29/expulsions-of-chinese-students-spread-confusion-from-yale-to-uva</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自去年 11 月以来，美国机场海关人员已禁止至少 20 名持有效签证的学生和学者入境，这是已解散的“中国倡议”的“更阴险”版本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-05-29/expulsions-of-chinese-students-spread-confusion-from-yale-to-uva</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 04:01:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汤卡表示，欧盟各国政府需要在银行规则方面更加大胆</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/eu-governments-need-to-be-braver-on-banking-rules-toncar-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国副财政部长表示，欧盟的银行业野心是错误的，欧盟需要进行重新调整，以使银行更容易跨境运营。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/eu-governments-need-to-be-braver-on-banking-rules-toncar-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国财政部长坚持 2025 年预算限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/german-finance-minister-standing-firm-on-2025-budget-restraint</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据德国财政部长的一位副手透露，德国财政部长克里斯蒂安·林德纳 (Christian Lindner) 不会屈服于部分内阁同僚要求在明年预算中增加资金的恳求，并将坚定地坚持执行严格的借贷规则的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/german-finance-minister-standing-firm-on-2025-budget-restraint</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非即将迎来后种族隔离时代最激烈的选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/south-africa-election-may-place-anc-majority-at-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非周三举行的选举似乎将重塑由纳尔逊·曼德拉领导的政党主导了三十年的政治格局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/south-africa-election-may-place-anc-majority-at-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管经济形势乐观，但欧洲首席执行官认为与中国的关系正在恶化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/europe-ceos-see-china-ties-worsening-despite-economic-optimism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大多数欧洲商界领袖表示，由于贸易挑战和地缘政治气候加剧紧张局势，未来几年欧洲与中国的关系可能会恶化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/europe-ceos-see-china-ties-worsening-despite-economic-optimism</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国前总理他信将因侮辱王室被起诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/former-thai-leader-thaksin-indicted-in-royal-defamation-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国检察机关决定对前总理他信·西那瓦正式提起诽谤王室的指控，这给控制该国执政党的政治王朝领袖带来了新的法律风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/former-thai-leader-thaksin-indicted-in-royal-defamation-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 02:41:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>金正恩誓言发射更多间谍卫星，朝鲜向南方投放“污秽”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/kim-jong-un-pledges-to-put-satellites-in-sky-after-rocket-fails</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜领导人金正恩表示，部署间谍卫星对于保护朝鲜主权至关重要。此前，朝鲜一枚火箭在飞行中失败，朝鲜政权兑现了向韩国发射气球的威胁，向韩国投放“污秽物”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/kim-jong-un-pledges-to-put-satellites-in-sky-after-rocket-fails</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 00:45:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港首次实施国安法 针对天安门活动人士</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/hong-kong-makes-first-arrests-under-new-domestic-security-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港当局首次启用新国家安全法，表明即使在没有公开抗议的情况下，政府也打算继续打击所谓的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/hong-kong-makes-first-arrests-under-new-domestic-security-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 09:15:23 GMT</pubDate>
